Package: scistreer
Title: Maximum-Likelilihood Single-Cell Phylogeny At Scale
URL: https://github.com/kharchenkolab/rscistree
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Teng","Gao", email="tgao@g.harvard.edu", role=c("cre", "aut")), person("Evan", "Biederstedt", email="evan.biederstedt@gmail.com", role="aut"), person("Peter", "Kharchenko", email = "peter_kharchenko@hms.harvard.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: 'scistreer' is an R implementation of the Single Cell Infinite Sites Tree (ScisTree) algorithm <doi.org/10.1093/bioinformatics/btz676>. It improves scalability of the algorithm via RcppParallel and is applicable to very large single-cell datasets (>10,000 cells).
